# Development Instructions

## Quick Command Reference

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev-workflow` | Full workflow with auto-fix (REQUIRED after changes) |
| `npm run dev-workflow:check` | Check without auto-fix |
| `npm run dev-workflow:quick` | Skip tests |
| `npm run format` | Format with Prettier |
| `npm run format:check` | Check formatting |
| `npm run lint` | Lint with auto-fix |
| `npm run lint:check` | Lint check only |
| `npm run typecheck` | TypeScript type check |
| `npm run build` | Build with tsup |
| `npm run test` | Run tests |
| `npm run test:coverage` | Tests with coverage |

## constants-check CLI

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npx constants-check` | Analyze current directory |
| `npx constants-check --check` | Fail on duplicates (CI) |
| `npx constants-check --monorepo` | Analyze monorepo |
| `npx constants-check --cross-package` | Cross-package only |
| `npx constants-check --definitions-only` | Definitions only |
| `npx constants-check --format json` | JSON output |
